    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Chop your <strong>potato[es] </strong>(skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp \u2013 these are your <strong>crispy potatoes</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/flaked-salmon-tart-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, add your <strong>soured cream </strong>and<strong> dried oregano</strong> to a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a few grinds of <strong>black pepper </strong>\u2013<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>creamy base mixture</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/flaked-salmon-tart-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of<strong> flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry </strong>and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin </strong>and cut it into 1 rectangle per person</p><p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>pastry</strong> to the tray[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and score a 1cm border around the edge of your pastry with a knife</p><p>Tip: The pastry border will puff up to give you a nice crust!</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/flaked-salmon-tart-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Spread the <strong>creamy base mixture </strong>over the pastry (keep it within the borders!)</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/flaked-salmon-tart-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Top the creamy base mixture with your<strong> salmon flakes</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until the pastry is golden and crisp and the edges have puffed up \u2013 this is your <strong>flaked</strong> <strong>salmon tart</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/flaked-salmon-tart-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the tart is cooking, add your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> to a bowl with a generous drizzle of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/flaked-salmon-tart-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>salad </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>balsamic dressing </strong>and gently toss it all together \u2013 this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/flaked-salmon-tart-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> flaked salmon tart</strong> with the <strong>crispy potatoes</strong> and <strong>dressed salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
